  "category": "wet",
  "description": "Softened setup for reduced grip conditions. Lower aero dependency, gentler differential, and softer springs keep the car predictable in the wet.",
  "strengths": ["Predictable in low grip", "Gentle power delivery", "Good traction"],
  "weaknesses": ["Slower in dry conditions", "Less responsive turn-in"],
